'''巴约訥大桥'''（'''Bayonne Bridge'''）是世界上跨度第四长的[[钢铁|钢铁]][[拱桥|拱桥]]，落成时是世界上最长的。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.panynj.gov/bayonnebridge/ |title=Bayonne Bridge Navigational Clearance Program |work=Port Authority of New York and New Jersey |accessdate=July 4, 2011 |archive-date=2011-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628052710/http://www.panynj.gov/bayonnebridge/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=World's Longest Arch Span in Kill Van Kull Bridge |magazine=Popular Mechanics |page=471 |accessdate=January 8, 2010 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=deIDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA471 |date=September 1930 |archive-date=2014-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111152748/http://books.google.com/books?id=deIDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA471 |dead-url=no }}</ref>它連接[[美國|美國]][[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[巴約訥_(新澤西州)|貝約訥]]及[[纽约州|纽约州]][[斯塔腾岛|斯塔腾岛]]，跨越[[Kill_Van_Kull|Kill Van Kull]]。

